data.description: Serene and peaceful waterfront home only sharing one wall, nestled on Golden Pond. This home boasts three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a finished walkout basement. Conveniently located near US 23 and downtown Fenton ensures easy access to amenities while reveling in the peaceful ambiance of waterfront living. Discover the allure of waterfront living and experience the perfect harmony of nature and convenience in this stunning home on Golden Pond. There are no association fees!
